<body><bold>Blue Chitin Helmet<end>
<tab><BREEDING name=chitinHelmet domain=Hivetera nbt_string="PATTERN blue">
After the family had gotten raided for the third time by creatures in red helmets, the elders had had enough. They experimented with Clay Hunters in hopes to achieve the same red helmets. Instead, the clan created a blue colored helmet, with the help of the Clay Hunters' hardening secretion. They fell in love with the result, as it bore the blue color that represented their name 'Lapis Scarab'.   
